Nginx with Certbot to automatically enable HTTPS on your website. Powered by Let's Encrypt.

---

This image based on [nginx:mainline](https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx/).(NGINX_MAINLINE)
and contains [Nginx](http://nginx.org).(vNGINX_VERSION) and [Certbot](https://certbot.eff.org).(vCERTBOT_VERSION).

The main purpose of the image is to simplify work with HTTPS for multiple sites.
